snippet.title: Trollskog Trailer α
snippet.description:
Trollskog is now on Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=868324604

Trollskog is a folk-tale fantasy city-builder strategy game due to be released for Windows PC in 2017.

Awesome music by Shane Rutherfoord Jones - http://shanerjmusic.co.uk 

Sound effects by Tyler Kerr - https://tyler.bike
